data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome home to this newly 2021 built 2 story pool home. With 2721 Sqft of living this home is the perfect space for entertaining! The master bedroom suite is on the first floor and features a spacious luxury bathroom with walk in closet. On the second floor there is a spacious game room/loft common area and the 4 other bedrooms and 2 baths. Upon entering you will enjoy the open concept great room/nook/kitchen area. Kitchen comes complete with stainless steel appliances. There's also a powder room on the first floor for convenience of your guests. Whole home Solar Panels have been added, lowering electric payments year-round to only about $35/month. The outdoor space features a 14x28 heated saltwater pool with a screened enclosure, creating a relaxing oasis for your family to enjoy. ROOF 2021. POOL 2022. SOLAR PANELS 2022. Don't miss your chance to own this exceptional pool home that combines comfort and entertainment in a country setting. Put this home on your must visit list! Schedule your private showing today!
